{"tid":2233340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我憑我本事借嚟二萬億，點解要還？","createTime":"2020-10-07T05:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T05:17:00.000Z","uid":233098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff66963c8083ba0c1d0c9323508219e09034eff","tid":2233340,"uid":233098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"無論環境多艱難，作為大股東兼主席，許家印至今仍能獨善其身。持有101.6億股的他，根據今年恒大派人民幣 0.653 (相當於港元 0.71元）股息計算，<span class=\"red\">今年他收了72.15億港元股息，已比上年收取的160億元息少兩倍。</span>五年以來，恒大派息比率一直維持在50%或以上，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">五年派息金額共474.3億，許家印從中已袋408.88億元。</span></span>坐擁2,900億人民幣資產，早已超越馬雲和馬化騰成為中國首富。<br />\n<br />\n呢個故事教曉大家，有借有還係on9仔，完。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_761975_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_761975_0&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=56c504d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_761975_0&h=a65ab6c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_761975_0</a>"},{"pid":"79db5e197c65d086400c39ea70e85143c3e4f136","tid":2233340,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"到時應該好多人跳樓"}]}